title: Tensung FC
text:
Tensung FC is a <a href="Bhutan">Bhutanese</a> professional <a href="association%20football">football</a> club which competes in the <a href="Bhutan%20Premier%20League">Bhutan Premier League</a>, the top level of <a href="football%20in%20Bhutan">Bhutanese football</a>.
History.
In Tensung's first <a href="Thimphu%20League">Thimphu League</a> season in 2016, the club finished 7th with a goal difference of −28. They registered their first point in April, holding <a href="Thimphu%20FC">Thimphu FC</a> to a 0–0 draw.
